  "changelogHtml": "<h3 id=\"input-motionprediction-1.0.0-beta01\" data-text=\"Version 1.0.0-beta01\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 1.0.0-beta01</h3>\n<p>March 22, 2023</p>\n<p><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.input:input-motionprediction:1.0.0-beta01</code> is released. <a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/4a2f5e696614339c1ac21f706c1a17c0285780e7..5e7d256f82fbafb6d059ab7b18fddd87c7531553/input/input-motionprediction\">Version 1.0.0-beta01 contains these commits.</a></p>\n<p><strong>New Features</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Orientation and tilt are present in the predicted motion events</li>\n<li>Dynamically calculated prediction internals</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>API Changes</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Removed <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">close</code> method as it is no longer needed (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/#/q/I843491e06b583282a4a085737429c80bc6322d99\">I84349</a>)</li>\n</ul>",
